nding and project-specific behavior behind configuration or explicit extension boundary is allowed.","Add integration tests exercising prompt resolution, leaf and container scope routing, and production project fan-in via the real overlay loader and ProductionBatchRunner, proving existing behavior is unchanged when the overlay is absent."]},"digest_hash_version":1,"model":"claude-opus-4-8","schema":"ticket_digest_v1"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"TICKET_DIGEST","timestamp":1784169891747934001,"uuid":"8e4208b3-2ddf-4a4c-83e1-63a08410b7dc"}